overview.en: ZIS is the first eco-chain to establish a 3.0 cross-border trade payment chain. It is the payment and consumption scenario that is really applied to block life. It is issued with the domestic currency ZIS as the quota and the application of physical landing as the development starting point.
overview.zh: ZIS 是第一个建立3.0跨境贸易支付链条的生态链，以本国货币ZIS为限额发行，以实物登陆的应用为发展起点，打破传统的生活消费模式，是真正应用于街区生活的支付和消费场景。
